data.description: Welcome to this incredible 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom abode, where possibilities and charm unite! Marvel at the two inviting living areas adorned with charming wood beams and a cozy fireplace, making it the perfect sanctuary for cherished moments with loved ones. Nestled on a spacious lot, this home offers the perfect canvas to unleash your creativity and make it truly your own. Plus, with schools nearby, your family will enjoy the convenience of easy access to education and everything else. Call now
